title: ITV On Assignment 2016 Austria Tanzania and Estonia 720p x264 AA
description:
Austria, Tanzania and Estonia

Sociopolitical Documentary hosted by Rageh Omaar, published by ITV broadcasted as part of ITV On Assignment series in 2016 - English narration. 
http://docuwiki.net/images/8/8e/Austria-Tanzania-and-Estonia-Cover.jpg

Information
------------------------------
James Mates is in Austria where an imminent election could result in Europe's first far-right President since the Second World War. John Ray investigates the deadly and destructive practice of dynamite fishing in Tanzania. Simon Harris travels to Estonia to meet the Seto people - one of the last folk cultures in Europe.
